<div class="objective_text">
  <h2>General Loan</h2>
			<p>For the purpose of income generating activities of the clients, General Loan of Rs. 15000.00
				 is provided as first year loan.According to client's loan utility and regular repayment status Rs. 5000.00 is increased on the loan amount every year. The rate of interest on providing loan is 25.0 percent. Upto the last F/Y 2067/068 WSC has Rs. 71.44 million general loan outstanding.
				</p>
	<h2>Seasonal Loan</h2>
		 <p>If any loanee needed additional loan after taking General loan,she get seasonal loan. All the 				processes of providing loan, loan demand, recommedation, interest rate and attaining is like 	general loan process. Up to this F/Y total seasonal loan outstanding is Rs. 12.35 million.
			</p>
	<h2>Contingency Loan</h2>
			<p>This type of loan is provided to meet contingency events such as to pay the school fee of client's
					children and medical treatment of client's and their family. General loanee can get this loan maximum amount of Rs. 2000 for the five months of period. This types of loan is not for proposse of investment in income generating activities.
			</p>


